comment: Anyone else have a fun weekend?
well i am sick but i am ok
I... uh... I think I finally quit Apex Legends for the last time :ptv-uneasy:
I have my minor complaints overall about the game, but it's been out for how long and is still super unstable?
Yesterday, the game crashed under 3 different errors.  1 was a texture failed to load, 1 was DEVICE_HUNG (aka lost the video card), and the infamous CODE:LEAF
Like... I knew CODE:LEAF affected console players (seriously, even the console version isn't completely stable), but it affects PC as well??
I'm only interested in the game at all anymore because of ranked and any fun seasonal events

But it's impossible to climb higher right now due to how crash prone it is.  And they don't have a reconnect feature so if you disconnect for ANY reason, that match is done and if you didn't earn back your RP, well, tough shite
Btw, sunk 125 hours into the game, I'm pretty sure my complaints are valid at this point xD
It's not wasted time, if you had fun while playing, Noodle.
Also, I think the rumors about humans having a second stomach dedicated solely for dessert may be true. So much cake...
